snippet.title: First gameplay clip of our new game: Karting Superstars!
snippet.description:
Before they were Circuit Superstars, they were ✨Karting Superstars✨! We’re excited to announce our ode to the purest form of racing, a charming racing game that captures the exciting and competitive world of karting. Wishlist on Steam now! 

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2503220/Karting_Superstars/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=early-access
